data.description:
This property has beautiful topography! Seller has planted trees on property for privacy and added enjoyment. This is an "off the grid" cabin and a 
must see 6.093 acre lot. This cabin offers the perfect re-treat to enjoy natures most beautiful things. This piece of land allows for great views, hunting, hiking, camping, or just a place to get alway! The cozy cabin sits on top of the hill side with complete privacy!! Solar panels located on roof allows for the off grid experience! This cabin is heated with propane heater, located on wall of cabin. Rain collection barrel utilized for water supply. 
Slate table and benches will convey with sale of property, along with riding mower.
